linux for hvisor(loongarch64)

the goal is boot linux with fdt in hvisor zone without
modifying the kernel source code.

sudo apt install libncurses-dev flex bison bc

current supported root/nonroot linux kernel version: v6.13.7 (stable in 2025.3)

modify the `chosen` file to `6.13.7`/`git` to use the corresponding kernel version
